    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You charge toward undead and fiends with confidence in your righteous cause.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Base attack bonus +1, any good alignment.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You do not take a penalty to AC while charging undead creatures and evil outsiders.<br/><br/><b>Normal</b><br/>When you charge, you take a -2 penalty to AC until the start of your next turn.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When charging any creature with an evil alignment, you can spend 2 stamina points in order to ignore the -2 penalty to AC imposed by charging.",
